<plot>3 episode film starring popular comedians Franchi and Ingrassia. In the first episode, Carlo and Oreste are married to the same woman. When twins are born, they fight for paternity. In the 2nd episode, Celestina needs a heir to receive her dead husband's fortune. In the 3rd episode, young widow Daisy arrives in Italy to meet her old deceased husband's family and turns out marrying his great-grandson.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?202264</url></doc>
